    "created_at": "2017-07-12T16:29:26Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-07-12T16:29:26Z",
    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "@abcdefg30 Yes that is possible, but I don't see a reason not to fulfill this request.\r\n`SpawnActorOnDeath` being conditional and allowing multiple Actor types to be provided is the most flexible without requiring many `SpawnActorOnDeath` instances.\r\n\r\nThis needs discussion and a decision on how we're going to supply spawn offsets.\r\n\r\nThe path of least breakage would be `Offset` being refactored into `CVec[] Offsets` with a 1:1 relationship with `Actors`."
  },
